0.5.0 - 1 December 2015
=======================
    - drop South support
    - drop support for Django < 1.8, add support for Django 1.9

0.4.0 - 26 May 2015
====================
    - drop South support
    - drop support for Django < 1.7, add support for Django >= 1.7
    - add Python 3 support
    - add a ton of tests
    - fix bug if vote_name was set in enable_voting_on

